K12D0576=D0932_H0747:135b-1: a'arya pradzny'a p'a ra mi ta sha ta sa ha sra dh'a ra ni /
K12D0576=D0932_H0747:135b-3: 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stong phrag brgya pa'i gzungs /
K12D0576=D0932_H0747:135b-4: bcom ldan 'das ma yum shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12D0576=D0932_H0747:135b-10: s'a ra aa nu gra ha dharme /
K12D0576=D0932_H0747:136a-1: na pa ri brta na dharme /
K12D0576=D0932_H0747:136a-2: sarba k'arya pa ri pra ma na dharme /
K12D0576=D0932_H0747:136a-3: sa manta aa nu pa ri brta na dharme sv'ah'a /
K12D0576=D0932_H0747:136a-4: aom pra dzny'e shru ti smri ti ma ti bi dza ye sv'ah'a /
K12D0576=D0932_H0747:136a-5: dh'i: dh'a ra ni sv'ah'a; aom pradzny'a p'a ra mi t'a pa la sv'ah'a /
K12D0576=D0932_H0747:136a-6: 'di bzung bas shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stong phrag brgya pa gzung bar 'gyur ro //
K12D0576=D0932_H0747:136a-7: rtag tu bzlas brjod byas na yid gzhungs par 'gyur ro //
K12D0576=D0932_H0747:136a-8: las kyi sgrib pa thams cad byang bar 'gyur ro //
